These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, oliveros, game, alhambra
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the game-smoker is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Cigar      | alhambra  | prince | oliveros  | game |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, orchid, lily
1. the egyptian is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growslily##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Flower           | orchid      | marigold    | azalea | lily      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, lacrosse, snowboarding
1. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | snowboarding   | lacrosse | golf    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, ferret, fish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | ferret | goldfish | bird | fish |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

