.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, photographer, police-officer, designer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the designer is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the designer is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
3. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the designer is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Job          | police-officer | designer   | scientist   | photographer    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

