.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, pop, techno, hip-hop
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | hip-hop | techno     | jazz   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

