.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, french, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the french##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the brazilian##1
4. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the french is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian   | french | thai     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

