.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, woodworking, writing
City: boston, miami, liverpool, hannover
1. the person traveling to miami is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| City   | boston     | hannover  | miami  | liverpool    |

