There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | taxi | bike | scooter |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

