.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice | almond-milk  | milk      | hot-chocolate |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

