.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
House: townhouse, craftsman, tower, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the tower house is in an even position##4
2. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
6. the tower house is between the townhouse house and the fan of electronic##2
7. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| House      | townhouse   | tower  | craftsman      | farmhouse       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

