.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, poker, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person playing poker is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | domino     | canasta | scrabble | poker |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

