City: liverpool, berlin, hamburg, marseilles
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person traveling to berlin##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| City   | hamburg | marseilles  | liverpool | berlin        |

