.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, documentary, adventure, disaster
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the person watching zombie movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | disaster | documentary      | zombie        |

 